1️⃣ Network Security Tools
These tools monitor and protect network traffic.
Examples:
Wireshark
Used to capture and analyze network packets.
Helps identify suspicious traffic.
Snort
Detects attacks in network traffic.
Works as IDS/IPS.
Nmap
Scans networks and finds open ports.
Used for vulnerability discovery.
pfSense
Firewall and router for network protection.
📌 Example Use Case:
A company network admin uses Wireshark to analyze traffic and detect suspicious packets.
